@startuml DevOps_Lifecycle_Overview

left to right direction

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #374151
skinparam ArrowThickness 2

skinparam rectangle {
  FontColor #111827
  RoundCorner 10
  FontSize 11
}

rectangle "1 · PLAN\n...........\nGitHub Issues\nBranching Strategy\nDependabot config\nOpenAPI spec" as PLAN #E8F5E9
rectangle "2 · CODE\n...........\nFeature branches\nPull Request to main\nDependabot PRs\nGo + PostgreSQL" as CODE #E3F2FD
rectangle "3 · BUILD\n...........\ngo build\nDocker Buildx\nPush to GHCR\n:latest + :sha" as BUILD #FFF8E1
rectangle "4 · TEST\n...........\ngo vet + gofmt\ngolangci-lint\ngo test -race\nDB schema validation\nQuality Gate" as TEST #FCE4EC
rectangle "5 · RELEASE\n...........\nMerge to main\nGHCR image versioned\nworkflow_dispatch\nSmoke Test HTTP 200" as RELEASE #EDE7F6
rectangle "6 · DEPLOY\n...........\nSCP to Azure VM\ndocker compose up\nRestart nginx\ndeploy_compose.sh" as DEPLOY #E0F7FA
rectangle "7 · OPERATE\n...........\nAzure VM (app)\nDigitalOcean (monitoring)\nPostgreSQL + disk\nNginx TLS + fail2ban" as OPERATE #FFF3E0
rectangle "8 · MONITOR\n...........\nPrometheus scrape\nGrafana dashboards\nApp Down alert\nError Rate alert\nDiscord notify" as MONITOR #F3E5F5

PLAN    --> CODE
CODE    --> BUILD
BUILD   --> TEST
TEST    --> RELEASE
RELEASE --> DEPLOY
DEPLOY  --> OPERATE
OPERATE --> MONITOR
MONITOR ..> PLAN : feedback loop

@enduml
